lead_paragraph: Valencia coach Gary Neville described his team's 7-0 drubbing by Barcelona in the Spanish King's Cup semi-final first leg on Wednesday as one of his worst experiences in football.

headline.print_headline: Barcelona Mauling One of My Worst Experiences-Neville
